      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im 24 weeks pregnant and i have this insane sinus infection, like my head is pounding and i cant breathe through my nose at all. i have some Sudafed left over from before i was pregnant, is it okay to take a couple of those to help with the congestion or is that a bad idea?",
