      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait vitamin C wont really help with the actual sinus pressure though. i feel like i need something stronger than salt water if i'm gonna sleep tonight. what about an antibiotic like ciprofloxacin? my doctor mentioned it once for other infections, is that safe to take for a sinus thing while pregnant?",
